fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.hbase.util

Class HBaseEncoderUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.hbase.util.HBaseEncoderUtil

  • public class HBaseEncoderUtil
extends Object
    Utility class that is responsible of Object to Byte encoding. This class is used to ensure that HBase keys have the same size, and provides an uniformized API to encode strings and EReference.
